data.description: CLOSE TO SHOPPING, SCHOOLS, PARKS, EASY FREEWAY ACCESS.  This home has room for it all, kids, their toys, YOUR toys, crafts, storage space you'll never fill up!  The home has a luxurious feel to it with beautifully elevated ceilings and real hardwood flooring. Custom kitchen surrounds beautiful granite island with modern light fixtures. This kitchen is huge!  Four large bedrooms, 2 living spaces and a giant bonus room/man cave with built in cabinets for even more storage!   Advanced plumbing system, utility sink in laundry room & garage, two 50 gallon h20 heaters, garden tub & shower in second bath, 6' heated jetted tub in master, 5' shower w/2 heads, hot & cold water plumbed outside, Beautiful landscaping with an English country garden feel and lots of entertaining space, new deck in backyard, oversized 3-car garage with reinforced overheard garage shelving.  RV parking to accommodate a 36' Class A motor home.  Home Warranty included. NEW PLUSH CARPET INSTALLED IN LIVING/DINING ROOM.
